    Author:
    Code - Ricards Cacurs. Class representing Stacked Multiscale Feature extractor from paper: Adam Coates and Andrew Y. Ng "Learning Feature Representations with K-means", Neural Networks: Tricks of the Trade, 2nd edn, Springer, 2012.
